      "releaseNotes": "What's new in 4.0: \nEnhanced account authentication - Added a more secure method for logging in.\nImproved flow for saving birds - Streamlined the process for saving birds to your life list.\nAdded support for iOS 26.\nBug fixes and improvements.\n\nImportant Update Notice: You'll be automatically logged out when this version launches due to the new authentication system. Simply log back in using any login screen. Forgot your password? Use the reset option to get back in quickly.",
